 where the norms 
\begin_inset Formula $\norm{\cdot}_{V}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\norm{\cdot}_{W}$
\end_inset

 are 
\begin_inset Formula $\ell_{2}$
\end_inset

 norms if unspecified.
